original_title: Pussié Control: The Story Of Davion Pussié
overview: Davion Pussie is a hood-talking, video game-playing cat who has a tight bond with his sweet loving owner, Tiana. When Tiana decides to date a new man, who isn’t whom he appears to be, Davion warns her of his advances. Can Davion get to the bottom of his intentions before it spells disaster for his beloved pet owner and livelihood?
title: Pussié Control: The Story Of Davion Pussié
